data.description: LOWEST PRICED HOME in The Place -Welcome to paradise in this highly desirable community. This bright and well maintained VENICE model is ready for its new owner.  This beautiful home offers 3 bedrooms, 3 baths with a spacious open split floor plan. The kitchen is facing the dining and living room and has a big island, a walk-in pantry and each of the bedrooms has its own full bathroom.  Other features include crown molding, upgraded ceiling fans, a kitchen backsplash as well as smart / security equipment - 4 outdoor security cameras, a Nest smart lock, a Nest smart thermostat, a Wi-Fi access point and a Google hub.   The Place at Corkscrew is one of the most desired communities in Estero and boasts the ultimate resort lifestyle! Whether you love a zero entry resort style pool with a 100’ Waterslide, a splash pad, playground, a restaurant with an inside and an outside bar or a prestigious Bourbon Bar, a beautiful Fitness Center, Tennis, Bocce, Pickle ball, Volleyball or you just want to relax in the Café and Marketplace after your massage- The Place has it all!
